See: &lt;a class="ext-link" href="http://wiki.apache.org/solr/SimpleFacetParameters#facet.sort"&gt;&lt;span class="icon"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;http://wiki.apache.org/solr/SimpleFacetParameters#facet.sort&lt;/a&gt;
